name: PKPassLibraryAddPassesStatus
desc: Statuses that PassKit uses when it adds passes to the pass library.

items.name: case didAddPasses
items.desc: A status that occurs when the user successfully adds one or more passes.

items.name: case shouldReviewPasses
items.desc: A status that occurs when the app prompts the user to review the passes.

items.name: case didCancelAddPasses
items.desc: A status that occurs when the user cancels the addition of passes.
